---

---

<section
    class="med-section med-section-local"
>
    <div class="med-absolute med-inset-0 med-pointer-events-none med-opacity-10">
        <svg class="med-w-full med-h-full">
            <pattern
                id="spiralPattern"
                x="0"
                y="0"
                width="100"
                height="100"
                patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse"
            >
                <path d="M 50 50 Q 80 50 80 80" fill="none" stroke="#6366f1" stroke-width="1"
                ></path>
            </pattern>
            <rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="#312e81" filter="url(#spiralPattern)"></rect>
        </svg>
    </div>

    <div class="med-container">
        <div class="med-grid">
            <div class="med-info-column">
                <span
                    class="med-tag med-tag-local"
                    >La Firma de Dios</span
                >
                <h2 class="med-title med-title-local">
                    La Proporción Áurea
                </h2>

                <p class="med-description med-description-local">
                    ¿Se puede medir la belleza? Los griegos creían que sí. Un número irracional
                    (1,618...) que aparece en las galaxias, en las flores y en tu propio ADN.
                </p>

                <div
                    class="med-card med-card-local"
                >
                    <h3 class="med-card-title med-card-title-local">Phi (φ)</h3>
                    <p class="med-card-text med-card-text-local">
                        No es una invención humana, es una eficiencia de la naturaleza. Es la forma
                        óptima de empaquetar semillas en un girasol o brazos en una espiral
                        galáctica.
                    </p>
                    <p class="med-card-note med-card-note-local">
                        Medir el mundo es descubrir que el caos tiene reglas secretas.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="med-visual-column med-visual-column-local">
                <div class="med-visual-wrapper">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 400 300" class="med-w-full med-h-full med-overflow-visible">
                        <g stroke="#6366f1" stroke-width="1" fill="none" opacity="0.5">
                            <rect x="100" y="50" width="200" height="200"></rect>

                            <rect x="300" y="50" width="123.6" height="200"></rect>

                            <rect x="300" y="50" width="123.6" height="123.6"></rect>
                            <rect x="300" y="173.6" width="76.4" height="76.4"></rect>
                        </g>

                        <path
                            d="M 200 180 
                                 Q 210 180 210 190
                                 Q 210 200 200 200
                                 Q 180 200 180 180
                                 Q 180 150 210 150
                                 Q 250 150 250 190
                                 Q 250 250 190 250
                                 Q 100 250 100 160
                                 Q 100 50 250 50"
                            fill="none"
                            stroke="#c7d2fe"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            class="animate-draw-spiral"></path>

                        <g opacity="0.1" fill="#818cf8">
                            <circle cx="200" cy="190" r="2"></circle>
                            <circle cx="210" cy="185" r="3"></circle>
                            <circle cx="220" cy="170" r="5"></circle>
                            <circle cx="230" cy="140" r="8"></circle>
                        </g>
                    </svg>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .med-section-local {
        background-color: #1e1b4b;
        color: #e0e7ff;
    }

    .med-tag-local {
        color: #818cf8;
        border-color: #4338ca;
    }

    .med-title-local {
        color: #c7d2fe;
    }

    .med-description-local {
        color: #a5b4fc;
        opacity: 0.9;
    }

    .med-card-title-local {
        color: #e0e7ff;
    }

    .med-card-text-local {
        color: #c7d2fe;
    }

    .med-card-note-local {
        color: #818cf8;
    }

    .med-visual-column-local {
        height: 400px;
    }

    .med-card-local {
        background-color: color-mix(in srgb, #312e81 50%, transparent);
        border-color: #6366f1;
    }

    @keyframes drawSpiral {
        0% {
            stroke-dasharray: 1000;
            stroke-dashoffset: 1000;
        }
        100% {
            stroke-dasharray: 1000;
            stroke-dashoffset: 0;
        }
    }
    .animate-draw-spiral {
        animation: drawSpiral 5s ease-out infinite;
    }
</style>
